      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        BESI-C brings together the creative, problem-solving spirit of both
        engineering and nursing, and represents a truly interdisciplinary
        research endeavor supported by a dedicated team of faculty, students and
        collaborators.
      </p>

